Soft seeding — pooled stake calc, 10/day × 180d × 500 runs/cell
4 softs each get ~17.5% of bets, target = seed_pct × current pool, scales as pool grows.
Arb-out trigger: balance > 2.0× target → sweep excess to unlimited.
Refill trigger:  balance < 0.5× target → top up from unlimited.


